'''Krelk''' was an [[Askhew]] [[Chief/Legends|Chieftain]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Entooine]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. He was introduced to a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] by [[A-3P0]] whom agreed to help him stop [[Jowart Typok]] hunting the [[Blue bantha]]s. He accompanied them out of the base where they came across two adult banthas who had had their horns removed already as well as a young bantha. He communicated with the young blue bantha by approaching it with an ordinary [[Bantha/Legends|bantha's]] lower leg bone. The bantha informed him that the hunter was still close by.

